<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> - UTEC</title>
    
    <!-- Tailwind CSS Local -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/tailwind.css">
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- FontAwesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <!-- AOS Animations -->
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --utec-primary: #1e3a8a;
            --utec-secondary: #3b82f6;
            --utec-accent: #06b6d4;
            --utec-success: #10b981;
            --utec-warning: #f59e0b;
            --utec-danger: #ef4444;
            --utec-dark: #1f2937;
            --utec-light: #f8fafc;
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--utec-dark);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
            padding-top: 80px; /* Espacio para el navbar fijo */
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .navbar {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--utec-primary) 0%, var(--utec-secondary) 100%);
            padding: 1rem 0;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .navbar .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 1rem;
            width: 100%;
            flex-wrap: nowrap;
            height: 100%;
        }
        
        .navbar-brand {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .brand-text {
            display: inline-block;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        
        .brand-text small {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        
        .navbar-nav {
            display: flex !important;
            flex-direction: row !important;
            align-items: center;
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            visibility: visible !important;
            opacity: 1 !important;
            white-space: nowrap;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .navbar-nav .nav-item {
            margin: 0 0.5rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .navbar-nav .nav-item.dropdown {
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .navbar-nav .nav-item.dropdown .dropdown-menu {
            position: absolute;
            top: 100%;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 9999;
        }
        
        .navbar-nav .nav-link {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) !important;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            display: block;
            visibility: visible !important;
            opacity: 1 !important;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
        
        .navbar-nav .nav-link:hover {
            color: white !important;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .btn-register {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .btn-register:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--utec-primary) 0%, var(--utec-secondary) 50%, var(--utec-accent) 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 6rem 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .hero-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1000 1000"><polygon fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)" points="0,1000 1000,0 1000,1000"/></svg>');
            background-size: cover;
        }
        
        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        
        .hero-title {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        
        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        
        .btn-hero {
            background: white;
            color: var(--utec-primary);
            border: none;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .btn-hero:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            background: var(--utec-light);
        }
        
        .features-section {
            padding: 5rem 0;
            background: white;
        }
        
        .feature-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            height: 100%;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }
        
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        
        .feature-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--utec-primary), var(--utec-secondary));
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            color: white;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }
        
        .feature-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--utec-dark);
        }
        
        .feature-description {
            color: #6b7280;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .stats-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--utec-dark) 0%, #374151 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 4rem 0;
        }
        
        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }
        
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--utec-accent);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .how-it-works {
            padding: 5rem 0;
            background: var(--utec-light);
        }
        
        .step-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            position: relative;
            height: 100%;
        }
        
        .step-number {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--utec-primary), var(--utec-secondary));
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--utec-primary) 0%, var(--utec-secondary) 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 4rem 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: var(--utec-dark);
            color: white;
            padding: 3rem 0 1rem;
        }
        
        .footer-content {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #374151;
            padding-bottom: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        
        .footer-bottom {
            text-align: center;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }
        
        .social-links a {
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 0 0.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .social-links a:hover {
            color: var(--utec-accent);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        
        /* Estilos para dropdown manual */
        .dropdown-menu {
            display: none;
            position: absolute;
            top: 100%;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 9999;
            min-width: 200px;
            padding: 0.5rem 0;
            margin: 0.125rem 0 0;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #212529;
            text-align: left;
            list-style: none;
            background-color: #fff;
            background-clip: padding-box;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            border-radius: 0.375rem;
            box-shadow: 0 0.5rem 1rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.175);
        }
        
        .dropdown-menu.show {
            display: block;
        }
        
        /* Estilos para el menú colapsable */
        .navbar-toggler {
            display: none !important;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .navbar-collapse {
            display: flex !important;
            flex-direction: row !important;
            align-items: center !important;
            width: auto !important;
            height: auto !important;
            position: static !important;
            background: none !important;
            box-shadow: none !important;
            padding: 0 !important;
            margin-left: auto !important;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        /* Estilos para desktop */
        @media (min-width: 769px) {
            .navbar-collapse {
                display: flex !important;
                flex-direction: row !important;
                align-items: center !important;
                width: auto !important;
                height: auto !important;
                position: static !important;
                background: none !important;
                box-shadow: none !important;
                padding: 0 !important;
                margin-left: auto !important;
            }
            
            .navbar-nav {
                flex-direction: row !important;
                width: auto !important;
                display: flex !important;
                align-items: center !important;
            }
            
            .navbar-nav .nav-item {
                margin: 0 0.5rem !important;
                width: auto !important;
                display: inline-block !important;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .navbar-toggler {
                display: block !important;
            }
            
            .navbar-collapse {
                display: none !important;
                position: absolute;
                top: 100%;
                left: 0;
                right: 0;
                background: var(--utec-primary);
                flex-direction: column;
                padding: 1rem;
                box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
                z-index: 1000;
            }
            
            .navbar-collapse.show {
                display: flex !important;
            }
            
            .navbar-nav {
                flex-direction: column !important;
                width: 100%;
            }
            
            .navbar-nav .nav-item {
                margin: 0.5rem 0;
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
        
        .dropdown-item {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.375rem 1rem;
            clear: both;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #212529;
            text-align: inherit;
            text-decoration: none;
            white-space: nowrap;
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 0;
            transition: color 0.15s ease-in-out, background-color 0.15s ease-in-out;
        }
        
        .dropdown-item:hover {
            color: #1e2125;
            background-color: #e9ecef;
        }
        
        .dropdown-divider {
            height: 0;
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
            border: 0;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-title {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            
            .hero-section {
                padding: 4rem 0;
            }
            
            .feature-card {
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
                <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap me-2"></i>
                <span class="brand-text">
                    <strong>MATRICULATEC</strong>
                </span>
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" onclick="toggleMenu()">
                <i class="fas fa-bars"></i>
            </button>
            <div class="navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#inicio">Inicio</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#caracteristicas">Características</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#como-funciona">Cómo Funciona</a>
                    </li>
                    <% if (typeof isAuthenticated !== 'undefined' && isAuthenticated) { %>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/materias">
                                <i class="fas fa-book me-1"></i>
                                Materias
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/elegibilidad">
                                <i class="fas fa-check-circle me-1"></i>
                                Elegibilidad
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                            <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" onclick="toggleDropdown(event)">
                                <i class="fas fa-user me-1"></i>
                                <%= usuario.nombre %>
                            </a>
                            <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/dashboard">Mi Dashboard</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/auth/perfil">Mi Perfil</a></li>
                                <li><hr class="dropdown-divider"></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/auth/logout">Cerrar Sesión</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/auth/login">Iniciar Sesión</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link btn-register" href="/auth/registro">Registrarse</a>
                        </li>
                    <% } %>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section" id="inicio">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-6 hero-content" data-aos="fade-right">
                    <h1 class="hero-title">MATRICULATEC - Tu Gestor Académico Inteligente</h1>
                    <p class="hero-subtitle">
                        Desarrollado por <strong>UTEC</strong> para transformar tu experiencia universitaria. 
                        Gestiona tu progreso académico de manera inteligente, verifica requisitos previos 
                        y optimiza tu trayectoria en la Universidad Tecnológica del Uruguay.
                    </p>
                    <div class="d-flex gap-3 flex-wrap">
                        <% if (typeof isAuthenticated !== 'undefined' && isAuthenticated) { %>
                            <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-hero">
                                <i class="fas fa-home me-2"></i>
                                Ir al Dashboard
                            </a>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <a href="/auth/registro" class="btn btn-hero">
                                <i class="fas fa-user-plus me-2"></i>
                                Comenzar Ahora
                            </a>
                        <% } %>
                        <a href="#como-funciona" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg">
                            <i class="fas fa-play me-2"></i>
                            Ver Demo
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6" data-aos="fade-left">
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-chart-line" style="font-size: 15rem; opacity: 0.2;"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="features-section" id="caracteristicas">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row text-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto" data-aos="fade-up">
                                         <h2 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3">Características Principales</h2>
                     <p class="lead text-muted">
                         Descubre cómo MATRICULATEC, desarrollado por UTEC, puede transformar tu experiencia académica
                     </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="feature-title">Verificación Automática</h3>
                        <p class="feature-description">
                            Verifica automáticamente si cumples con los requisitos previos para cursar cualquier materia.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="feature-title">Planificación Inteligente</h3>
                        <p class="feature-description">
                            Planifica tu semestre de manera óptima basándote en tu progreso académico actual.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="feature-title">Seguimiento de Progreso</h3>
                        <p class="feature-description">
                            Monitorea tu avance académico con estadísticas detalladas y visualizaciones claras.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="feature-title">Seguridad Garantizada</h3>
                        <p class="feature-description">
                            Tus datos académicos están protegidos con las más altas medidas de seguridad.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="feature-title">Acceso Móvil</h3>
                        <p class="feature-description">
                            Accede a tu información académica desde cualquier dispositivo, en cualquier momento.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="feature-title">Soporte Académico</h3>
                        <p class="feature-description">
                            Recibe orientación personalizada para optimizar tu trayectoria universitaria.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Stats Section -->
    <section class="stats-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number" data-count="6">0</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Semestres</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number" data-count="32">0</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Materias</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number" data-count="77">0</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Previas</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number" data-count="100">0</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">% Confiable</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works Section -->
    <section class="how-it-works" id="como-funciona">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row text-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto" data-aos="fade-up">
                                         <h2 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3">¿Cómo Funciona?</h2>
                     <p class="lead text-muted">
                         Tres pasos simples para optimizar tu progreso académico en UTEC
                     </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="step-card">
                        <div class="step-number">1</div>
                        <h4 class="mb-3">Regístrate</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted">
                            Crea tu cuenta con tu información académica y accede al sistema.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <div class="step-card">
                        <div class="step-number">2</div>
                        <h4 class="mb-3">Verifica Elegibilidad</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted">
                            El sistema verifica automáticamente qué materias puedes cursar.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <div class="step-card">
                        <div class="step-number">3</div>
                        <h4 class="mb-3">Planifica tu Semestre</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted">
                            Recibe recomendaciones personalizadas para optimizar tu carga académica.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-lg-8 text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
                                         <h2 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-4">¿Listo para Transformar tu Experiencia en UTEC?</h2>
                     <p class="lead mb-4">
